snippet.title: Billie Jean So Gorgeous
snippet.description:
Hey yalllllll I am Billie Jean🤗 I am currently 25 years old. I live in Washington DC, although i was born and raised in North Carolina! ❤️ I love make up, hair, music, fashion, challenges, reporting the latest news in pop culture, telling hilarious stories, eating, vlogging & more! With my vibrant personality & radical lifestyle and experiences i aspire to  inspire millions of people around the world through YouTube✨check out my playlists for different videos !!

HIT THAT SUBSCRIBE BUTTON TO JOIN THE #GORGEOUSGANG 😍

Instagram/Tiktok: @BillieJeanSoGorgeous ❤️
